name: Cyberpunk Run (ishaan tailor 218881060)
description:
WELCOME TO CYBERPUNK RUN

This game was created for a school project where I've learned many skills and how to make a simple game.

In  this game you are a simple runner in a night life cyberpunk city avoiding enemies and trying to collect gems. Be careful because if you go below 0 points you lose. You also need 100 points to win.

Ishaan Tailor 218881060
